The heading, "Archline-BIM/CAD Services  
for the Building Industry", appears on top of the referenced blog below.  
Also appearing on this page is a link to "Archline Record". The  
term"Archline", is protected by a United States Federal Service Mark,  
issued by the US Patent Office. Archline CAD Services, Ltd. owns that  
Service Mark, #3,417,229. Greg H. Traylor has not been given,and will NOT 

be given, permission to use this Service Mark. As CEO and Founder of  
Archline I respectfully request that these offending references be deleted
 
from the Internet immediately.
